These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: poker, go
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia
There 2 different types of food: carrot, blueberry
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, turkish
1. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the right of the turkish##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Game       | go       | poker |
| Flower         | begonia | orchid  |
| Food       | blueberry    | carrot    |
| Nationality   | turkish       | chinese      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: whist, backgammon
House: craftsman, farmhouse
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: funk, trance
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, subway
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
3. the fan of funk is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Game      | backgammon     | whist |
| House           | craftsman | farmhouse      |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | funk      |
| Transport         | taxi | subway     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, dancing
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, biathlon
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani
City: hamburg, colone
1. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Hobby      | chess | dancing  |
| Sport          | sailing    | biathlon   |
| Cigar   | bongani  | ritmeester   |
| City     | colone     | hamburg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, dahlia
2 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly
City: new-york, miami
2 different pets are kept: horse, snake
1. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Flower      | sunflower       | dahlia |
| Game          | monopoly         | backgammon    |
| City           | miami | new-york    |
| Pet   | horse           | snake   |

