.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, march
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, coral
2 different games are played: backgammon, bridge
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, british
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the british##1
3. the person playing backgammon is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Birthday           | march | october     |
| Color   | blue          | coral |
| Game           | backgammon          | bridge    |
| Nationality     | british            | pakistani       |

 